  "projectName": "RemoteTerm for MeshCore",
  "projectDescription": "A self-hosted web application that connects to MeshCore mesh radios via Serial, TCP, or BLE, providing a browser-based interface for messaging, packet capture, bots, MQTT forwarding, and network visualization.",
