  "keyFeatures": [
    "Connect to MeshCore radios via Serial, TCP, or BLE",
    "Send and receive direct messages and channel messages in a browser UI",
    "Store-and-decrypt: cache all received packets and decrypt as keys are added",
    "Python bot system for automated message analysis and responses",
    "MQTT forwarding to private brokers, community mesh, and Home Assistant",
    "WebGPU-accelerated channel key brute-force cracker",
    "Network visualization via map view and force-directed topology graph",
    "Repeater telemetry monitoring and remote CLI management",
    "Web Push notifications for incoming messages (requires HTTPS)",
    "Fanout integrations: MQTT, webhooks, Apprise, Amazon SQS",
    "Store contacts and channels beyond radio hardware limits",
    "Systemd service and Docker deployment support"
  ],
